function、variable scope、data structures(List, Tuple, Dictionary, Stack)、string operation、file read/write、class/objects、recursion 呢 D 基本嘢入手"},{"pid":"14eb9bb43b26a306b8cb4194cd306d8e07e33b7e","tid":793481,"uid":98915,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08f4b9505c03ae069e192789817ed76496d89d68","tid":793481,"uid":68138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de19e135de1b17ea6bd7fe6e7215ffc8cb92a046","tid":793481,"uid":98915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"854a433f1298f5e6754b36e732132ef0b1a6e329","tid":793481,"uid":41243,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"Python關pure maths乜撚嘢事? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗matrix, linear algebra可能真係可能關少少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁python係有冇嘢要前提識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:24:05.000Z","msg":"要用腦, 你死左條心."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:40:06.000Z","msg":"你又知我冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能好勁呢"},{"pid":"80896d354ee18ba28ed8188935c660dbf654967f","tid":793481,"uid":98915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d88c0e0d1c865a65681a6230b069c229ed2ab06","tid":793481,"uid":72465,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"唔知巴打程度去到邊<br />\n<br />\n不過我認為 for 一個新手，用 Python 作為學 programming 嘅跳板係唔錯嘅選擇<br />\n唔使理個 language 常唔常用住，programming 有好多基本 concept 其實唔同 languages 係相通嘅，學咗嘅 concept 冇話會晒咗<br />\n<br />\n一般嚟講新手都係由條件式 (if...elif...else)、迴圈 (while, for ... in)、function、variable scope、data structures(List, Tuple, Dictionary, Stack)、string operation、file read/write、class/objects、recursion 呢 D 基本嘢入手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"Thz bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n立馬開波"},{"pid":"f350ff3c423f7b15d9313a83cc3033fd700bf548","tid":793481,"uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"學python要pure math底 唔係卦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1047a91234348f4ee54c7252485efbc01e08a8da","tid":793481,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89dd75b7df2ba4450b949639fda2f1a74f7683f8","tid":793481,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b9a2a3ad41532b9c2116ceae7177a6e701ece1e","tid":793481,"uid":72465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1047a91234348f4ee54c7252485efbc01e08a8da","tid":793481,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d88c0e0d1c865a65681a6230b069c229ed2ab06","tid":793481,"uid":72465,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"唔知巴打程度去到邊<br />\n<br />\n不過我認為 for 一個新手，用 Python 作為學 programming 嘅跳板係唔錯嘅選擇<br />\n唔使理個 language 常唔常用住，programming 有好多基本 concept 其實唔同 languages 係相通嘅，學咗嘅 concept 冇話會晒咗<br />\n<br />\n一般嚟講新手都係由條件式 (if...elif...else)、迴圈 (while, for ... in)、function、variable scope、data structures(List, Tuple, Dictionary, Stack)、string operation、file read/write、class/objects、recursion 呢 D 基本嘢入手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"視乎自己需要係乜。<br />\n<br />\nObject-oriented programming (OOP) 同埋基本 data structure (Stack/Queue) 呢 D 基本嘢都應該係必學嘅。<br />\n<br />\n去到咁上下基本上跳去學其他 programming languages，一般 D 基本嘢係相通嘅，所以上手會快好多。但係要學返 D syntax，同嘢唔同 programming languages 一 D specific 嘅 concept，例如 C++ 有 pointers、Java 嘅 lambda expression、GUI、唔同嘅 library 等等<br />\n<br />\n但係全部視乎自己需要。一般都係見到有問題唔識先會去學，唔係嘅話成個人 0 動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再深入 D 就 discrete maths、algorithms 、compiler 等等，但係都係睇有冇需要去到咁深入，有 D 太 theoretical 嘅嘢係 computer science major 先會學，好難自學返嚟。<br />\n<br />\n利申：非專業 有錯請大力屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a5c6fbbb08946ede36d2f70eb1de6385ddd0d5","tid":793481,"uid":72465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"其實最重要嘅係學到解決問題嘅能力<br />\nConcept 嘅嘢唔會太難明，但係點用返出嚟寫 programs 就極難<br />\n基本上係靠實戰經驗同不斷 debug，冇 short-cut<br />\n加埋大量繁瑣又不斷重複嘅嘢<br />\n所以真係要有興趣先好去馬，唔係好容易中途放棄"},{"pid":"8b371b6e8516539bcd289af78456f83f295f75a9","tid":793481,"uid":98915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15a5c6fbbb08946ede36d2f70eb1de6385ddd0d5","tid":793481,"uid":72465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"其實最重要嘅係學到解決問題嘅能力<br />\nConcept 嘅嘢唔會太難明，但係點用返出嚟寫 programs 就極難<br />\n基本上係靠實戰經驗同不斷 debug，冇 short-cut<br />\n加埋大量繁瑣又不斷重複嘅嘢<br />\n所以真係要有興趣先好去馬，唔係好容易中途放棄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:26:06.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d7fa98245fa016e352ee206588ffd064970441","tid":793481,"uid":5521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"玩瑪奇算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ecd30ba88361cf74bec0b5c054a6486c32868d","tid":793481,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70d7fa98245fa016e352ee206588ffd064970441","tid":793481,"uid":5521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"玩瑪奇算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 